{"tid":437423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【颱風接颱風】熱帶低壓蘭恩橫過菲國逐漸增強","createTime":"2017-10-16T03:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T09:25:08.000Z","uid":106675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f2a1523a0e2ef183063a7036b6e397b12c36cf03","tid":437423,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/paAJy7BnLSHP739Ma6hb4A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/89654193c17d2775fff3825f4c9dff77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpaAJy7BnLSHP739Ma6hb4A--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F89654193c17d2775fff3825f4c9dff77&h=3f42e08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港今早部分地區有雨。(何駿軒攝)<br />\n更多<br />\n強烈熱帶風暴「卡努」已減弱為熱帶風暴，已遠離香港。不過驟雨正影響華南沿岸，香港方面，今早(16日)新界部分地區錄得超過10毫米雨量，市民出外都係要帶定把遮。<br />\n<br />\n天文台在上午7時錄得氣溫27度，相對濕度95%，今日的最高紫外線指數大約是5，強度屬於中等。預測大致多雲，間中有驟雨，日間短暫時間有陽光，最高氣溫約28度，吹清勁偏東風，初時離岸及高地間中吹強風，海面有湧浪；展望未來數日天色逐漸好轉。<br />\n<br />\n熱帶風暴「卡努」目前集結在海口以西約70公里，預料向西南偏西移動，時速約15公里，橫過北部灣並減弱。另外，熱帶低氣壓「蘭恩」已增強為熱帶風暴，集結在雅蒲島之西北偏西約250公里，預料向西北移動，時速約15公里，橫過菲律賓以東海域並逐漸增強。"},{"pid":"9ba4e7fd2d877e0f9b13c953b0394538931cf6d3","tid":437423,"uid":141461,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"右 is me of tea cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc264b0334ae0d51ae2cf5bfec6690c20abcd5c","tid":437423,"uid":99962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>右 is me of tea cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/